OL,3,CCommunity praised for response to
OL,4,Cmajor Conwy Mountain wildfire
OL,6,FA community in Conwy is being praised
OL,7,Ffor their response to a major wildfire
OL,8,Fthat broke out near Conwy Mountain and
OL,9,Fthe Sychnant Pass on Sunday (12 July).
OL,11,FThe blaze has affected around 200
OL,12,Facres of land and some residents in
OL,13,Fthe village of Capelulo, near
OL,14,FPenmaenmawr in Conwy, have been told
OL,15,Fto evacuate their homes for safety.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
