OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1783952425
OL,3,CCommunity praised for response to
OL,4,Cmajor Conwy Mountain wildfire
OL,6,FPublic Health Wales urged people to
OL,7,Fstay indoors, turn off air
OL,8,Fconditioning systems that draw air in
OL,9,Ffrom outside, and if travelling
OL,10,Fthrough affected areas, try and keep
OL,11,Fvehicle windows closed.
OL,13,FGavin Parry, owner of The Gladstone
OL,14,Fpub in Deganwy, explained the quick
OL,15,Faction locals took to supporting
OL,16,Fpeople as soon as the wildfire emerged.
OL,18,F"When something goes wrong, the
OL,19,Fcommunity absolutely pulls together,"
OL,20,Fhe said.
