PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1783952425
OL,3,CCommunity praised for response to
OL,4,Cmajor Conwy Mountain wildfire
OL,6,F"We woke up in the early hours
OL,7,Fthinking there was a big sea mist but
OL,8,Fthere was a terrible smell, and then
OL,9,Fobviously to the news that there was a
OL,10,Ffire up on the mountain.
OL,12,F"We had communications from the local
OL,13,Frotary club who were already
OL,14,Fvolunteering. They had switched on
OL,15,Falmost immediately to the fire as some
OL,16,Fof them were based in Capelulo where
OL,17,Fit was most prevalent," Gavin told ITV
OL,18,FNews.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
