PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1783952425
OL,3,CCommunity praised for response to
OL,4,Cmajor Conwy Mountain wildfire
OL,6,F"The club were asking for support and
OL,7,Fwhat we could do to help, so we got
OL,8,Fstraight out there and started doing
OL,9,Fwhat we could do. We were trying to
OL,10,Fget water to the firefighters to keep
OL,11,Fthem hydrated. Rotary where already
OL,12,Frunning up the hill with kettles and
OL,13,Fjugs of water.
OL,15,F"Once people had realised what was
OL,16,Fgoing on, Facebook had gone off with
OL,17,Fall the businesses asking what they
OL,18,Fcould do."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
