OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1783952425
OL,3,CCommunity praised for response to
OL,4,Cmajor Conwy Mountain wildfire
OL,6,FJulie Fallon, Leader of Conwy Council,
OL,7,Fhas praised the work of locals who are
OL,8,Fsupporting those who have evacuated
OL,9,Ftheir homes.
OL,11,FShe said: "The fire has been very
OL,12,Fscary for local residents, but it's an
OL,13,Fopportunity to see a community come
OL,14,Ftogether in such an amazing way: be
OL,15,Fthat the locals, the fire service, the
OL,16,Fpolice service and Conwy Council as
OL,17,Fwell.
OL,26,@sD@KOU
