CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1783952425
OL,3,CCommunity praised for response to
OL,4,Cmajor Conwy Mountain wildfire
OL,6,F"The Council has instigated the
OL,7,Frespite that we have - we've got a
OL,8,Frespite centre over in Llandudno
OL,9,FJunction in the business centre, so
OL,10,Fthat's supporting families mainly to
OL,11,Fhelp them to move on if they've needed
OL,12,Faccommodation which we've organised.
OL,14,F"Staff have been amazing. There were
OL,15,Fso many people volunteering to help in
OL,16,Fthe respite centre, getting in touch
OL,17,Fsaying they can come in overnight and
OL,18,Fsupport."
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@IO]
