OL,3,CCommunity praised for response to
OL,4,Cmajor Conwy Mountain wildfire
OL,6,FIn a statement, North Wales Fire and
OL,7,FRescue service Head of Prevention,
OL,8,FJody McEacherm said: "Firefighters
OL,9,Fworked tirelessly throughout yesterday
OL,10,Fand overnight responding to a number
OL,11,Fof significant wildfire incidents
OL,12,Facross North Wales.
OL,14,F"Significant work continues at Conwy
OL,15,FMountain and we will continue to
OL,16,Fmonitor conditions closely throughout
OL,17,Fthe day.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/8
