OL,3,CCommunity praised for response to
OL,4,Cmajor Conwy Mountain wildfire
OL,6,F"I would like to thank local
OL,7,Fcommunities for their patience and co-
OL,8,Foperation, and our firefighters,
OL,9,FControl Room staff, partner agencies
OL,10,Ffor their ongoing support."
